worked great for me. Kapersky 2012 doesn't detect any threats so there isn't any viruses. Norton thinks everything is a threat and thats why i never use them. Let me tell you guys what worked for me since nobody else seems to answering questions around here.
Follow the install document file. Install the moviestudiope11.0.295.suite file followed by the audiostudio10.0.177 just like it says. Now STOP!!!

IGNORE THE KEYGEN FOLDER. Seems as though it didn't work for anyone including me. So click the Patch app, mine showed up as a key icon. RIGHT click and Run as Administrator in Windows. That part is crucial or it won't work. You think it might but it really won't. I made this mistake.

Now the window that shows up is really stupid and confusing in my opinion so I clicked on the guys website to get some info. After going there and translating the French with Google I found out all you gotta do is click the panther, or whatever the hell it is, on the LEFT. The little box below him will say Reg and then OK when its done. And so are you. Just exit and the program worked fine for me. Hope it does for your too. Enjoy guys
